  "title": "Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Supervisor</strong></p>\n<p>(Building Construction/Project)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>to assist in Project team on site matters</li>\n  <li>on building projects assigned</li>\n  <li>on maintenance and defects, A&amp;A works</li>\n  <li>co-ordination of sub-contractors and suppliers</li>\n  <li>able to lead &amp; supervise workers on site</li>\n  <li>comply with the site works and safety regulations and rules</li>\n  <li>daily ferrying workers to-&amp;-fro from dormitory to site</li>\n  <li>supervising of direct workforce on day-to-day operation of project</li>\n  <li>any other works as &amp; when directed by the Management or your Superior</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Recognized or related work skill certificates</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1 to 2 years construction trade experiences in Singapore</li>\n  <li>Candidate with no experience is welcome to apply</li>\n  <li>Preferred Singaporean to apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
